NEW TUTORIAL_EMPIREVIEW_FACTIONS_DESC:4 "The §SFactions§! screen gives an overview of the populace's political leanings. Be aware that shifts in the sociopolitical climate may give rise to §SFactions§!. Details on §SFaction§! sizes, attractiveness to our Pops, and how content they are may also be found here.\n\n§SFactions§! have §SIssues§! that are important to their overall §SApproval§!, and our policies and actions as a nation may displease or please these groupings, providing an increasing boost to £unity£§YUnity§! generation. The strength of §SFactions§! and the nature of their §SIssues§! can change along with our circumstances, but keep in mind that the §SHappiness§! of a §SPop§! can be affected by the §SApproval§! of the §SFaction§! it belongs to.\n\nWe can also §SManage Factions§! to manipulate the relationship between a §SFaction§! and the state, even going so far as embracing the ethos of a strong §SFaction§!."
OLD TUTORIAL_EMPIREVIEW_FACTIONS_DESC:3 "The §SFactions§! screen gives an overview of the populace's political leanings. Be aware that shifts in the sociopolitical climate may give rise to §SFactions§!. Details on §SFaction§! sizes, attractiveness to our Pops, and how content they are may also be found here.\n\n§SFactions§! have §SIssues§! that are important to their overall §SApproval§!, and our policies and actions as a nation may displease or please these groupings, providing an increasing boost to £influence£ §SInfluence§! generation. The strength of §SFactions§! and the nature of their §SIssues§! can change along with our circumstances, but keep in mind that the §SHappiness§! of a §SPop§! can be affected by the §SApproval§! of the §SFaction§! it belongs to.\n\nWe can also §SManage Factions§! to manipulate the relationship between a §SFaction§! and the state, even going so far as embracing the ethos of a strong §SFaction§!."
CN  TUTORIAL_EMPIREVIEW_FACTIONS_DESC:4 "§S党派§!界面显示了人口政治倾向的概览。注意社会政治气氛的变化可能会产生新的§S党派§!。这里也显示了§S党派§!规模，对我们人口的吸引力，以及派系满意程度的细节。\n\n§S党派§!有自己的§S议题§!，这对他们的§S赞同度§!有着很大的影响，而我们国家的政策与行动可能会惹恼或取悦这些团体，增加£influence£ §S影响力§!的产出。§S党派§!的实力与其§S议题§!的性质会随着状况发生改变，但记住§S人口§!的§S幸福度§!会受到其所属§S党派§!的§S赞同度§!影响。\n\n我们也可以用§S管理党派§!来调整某个§S党派§!与国家之间的关系，甚至接纳某个强大§S党派§!的思潮。"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_EMPIREVIEW_FACTIONS_DESC:4 "§S派系§!界面显示了人口政治倾向的概览。注意社会政治气氛的变化可能会产生新的§S派系§!。这里也显示了§S派系§!规模，对我们人口的吸引力，以及派系满意程度的细节。\n\n§S派系§!有自己的§S诉求§!，这对他们的§S赞同度§!有着很大的影响，而我们国家的政策与行动可能会惹恼或取悦这些团体，增加£unity£§Y凝聚力§!的产出。§S派系§!的实力与其§S诉求§!的性质会随着状况发生改变，但记住§S人口§!的§S幸福度§!会受到其所属§S派系§!的§S赞同度§!影响。\n\n我们也可以用§S管理派系§!来调整某个§S派系§!与国家之间的关系，甚至接纳某个强大§S派系§!的思潮。"
NEW TUTORIAL_TRADITIONS_SELECT_DESC:1 "This screen displays all the §HTradition trees§! available to our empire. Here you can check all the §HTraditions§! in each tree as well as the §Hadoption§! and §Hfinisher effects§!.\n\nI recommended some of the §HTradition trees§! for you to start."
