NEW TUTORIAL_EMPIRE_SPRAWL_DESC:1 "§H$EMPIRE_SIZE$§! is a measure of the territorial expanse of your empire in the form of controlled Systems, Colonies, Districts, and Total Population.\n\nA high Empire Sprawl is a strain on your empire's §SAdministrative Capacity§!, and will increase the cost of §STechnologies§!, §STraditions§!, §SLeaders§!, and §SEdicts§!"
OLD TUTORIAL_EMPIRE_SPRAWL_DESC:0 "§HEmpire Sprawl§! is a measure of the territorial expanse of your empire in the form of controlled Systems, Colonies, Districts, and Total Population.\n\nA high Empire Sprawl is a strain on your empire's §SAdministrative Capacity§!, and will increase the cost of §STechnologies§!, §STraditions§!, §SLeaders§!, and §SEdicts§!"
CN  TUTORIAL_EMPIRE_SPRAWL_DESC:1 "§H帝国规模§!是衡量帝国所控制的领土，包括控制的星系、殖民地、地区和总人口的指数。\n\n帝国规模过大会对帝国的§S行政容量§!形成压力，提高§S科技§!、§S传统§!、§S领袖§!和§S法令§!的费用。"
CHANGE TUTORIAL_EMPIRE_SPRAWL_DESC:1 "§H$EMPIRE_SIZE$§!是量化衡量帝国所控制的领土，其依据包括控制的恒星系、殖民地、区划及总人口的多少。\n\n帝国规模过大会对帝国的§S行政管理能力§!形成压力，并将提高§S科技§!、§S传统§!、§S领袖§!以及§S法令§!的花费。"
NEW tutorial.2007.desc:1 "We have made First Contact with a different type of civilization - one which is generally unwilling to engage in §SDiplomacy§! with others.\n\nThe diplomatic actions we can take with civilizations like this are limited, however they may decide to contact us from time to time."
