NEW tutorial_10_chain_desc:2 "We may want to consider recruiting another §SScientist§! to command our new §SScience Ship§!. A Science Ship cannot perform survey missions or research §SAnomalies§! without a Scientist.\n\nSelect our new Science Ship, and then click on the §SAssign Leader§! box. The §SLeaders§! tab will open, showing all Scientists currently employed by us. Click on the §SRecruit§! button at the top of this list.\n\nSelect the candidate you want, and click on their associated §SRecruit§! button. Recruiting a Leader costs £unity£§YUnity§!, and you may need to wait until you have enough stored.\n\nOnce recruited, the new Scientist will be ready for assignment on our homeworld."
OLD tutorial_10_chain_desc:1 "We may want to consider recruiting another §SScientist§! to command our new §SScience Ship§!. A Science Ship cannot perform survey missions or research §SAnomalies§! without a Scientist.\n\nSelect our new Science Ship, and then click on the §SAssign Leader§! box. The §SLeaders§! tab will open, showing all Scientists currently employed by us. Click on the §SRecruit§! button at the top of this list.\n\nSelect the candidate you want, and click on their associated §SRecruit§! button. Recruiting a Leader costs §SEnergy Credits§!, and you may need to wait until you have enough stored.\n\nOnce recruited, the new Scientist will be ready for assignment on our homeworld."
CN  tutorial_10_chain_desc:2 "我们应当考虑雇佣另外一名§S科学家§!指挥新§S科研船§!。科研船无法在没有科学家的情况下执行勘察任务或研究§S异常现象§! 。\n\n选择我们新的科研船，点击§S指派领袖§!。§S领袖§!页面会展开，展示为我们服务的所有科学家。在列表顶部点击§S招募§!按钮。\n\n选择你想要的科学家，然后点击§S招募§!按钮。招募领导会花费§S能量点数§!，请务必储存足够。\n\n招募完毕后，新的科学家便会在母星中等待部署。"
CHANGE tutorial_10_chain_desc:2 "我们或许应当考虑雇佣一名新的§S科学家§!来指挥全新的§S科研船§!。没有科学家指挥，科研船无法执行探索任务或是研究§S异常现象§!。\n\n选择我们的新科研船，点击§S指派领袖§!。§S领袖§!页面会展开，显示为我们服务的所有科学家。在列表顶部点击§S招募§!按钮。\n\n选择你想要的科学家，然后点击§S招募§!按钮。招募领袖会花费£unity£§Y凝聚力§!，您或需要等待这项资源储存至足量。\n\n招募完毕后，新的科学家便会在母星中等待安排。"
NEW tutorial_13_chain_desc:1 "We should recruit a §SPlanetary Governor§! to administer our new colony. To do this, click on the colony and go into its §SPlanet Summary§! tab. Then click on the §SChange§! button in the §SGovernor§! window. This will open the §SLeaders§! screen, showing the Governors currently working for us.\n\nClick on the §SRecruit§! button in the upper portion of the screen, and select from among the available candidates. Note that Leaders always cost £unity£§YUnity§! to recruit. If we lack the needed amount, we will have to wait until enough has been generated to afford the leader.\n\nOnce recruited, the new Governor will be awaiting assignment on our homeworld."
OLD tutorial_13_chain_desc:0 "We should recruit a §SPlanetary Governor§! to administer our new colony. To do this, click on the colony and go into its §SPlanet Summary§! tab. Then click on the §SChange§! button in the §SGovernor§! window. This will open the §SLeaders§! screen, showing the Governors currently working for us.\n\nClick on the §SRecruit§! button in the upper portion of the screen, and select from among the available candidates. Note that leaders always cost §SInfluence§! to recruit. If we lack the needed amount, we will have to wait until enough has been generated to afford the leader.\n\nOnce recruited, the new Governor will be awaiting assignment on our homeworld."
CN  tutorial_13_chain_desc:1 "我们需要招募一名§S行星总督§!来管理我们新的殖民地。要进行招募，点击殖民地，进入到§S行星总结§!标签中，在§S总督§!窗口点击§S改变§!按钮。此时会展开一个 §S领袖§!窗口，显示现在为我们工作的总督。\n\n在屏幕上方点击§S招募§!按钮，选择一名可供使用的总督。注意，招募领导会花费§S影响力§!。如果影响力不足，就要等到收集足够影响力后再进行招募。\n\n新总督招募完毕后将会在母星等待部署。"
CHANGE tutorial_13_chain_desc:1 "我们需要招募一名§S行星总督§!来管理我们新的殖民地。要进行招募，点击殖民地，进入到§S行星总览§!标签中，在§S总督§!窗口点击§S更换§!按钮。此时会展开一个§S领袖§!窗口，显示现在为我们工作的总督。\n\n在屏幕上方点击§S招募§!按钮，选择一名可供使用的总督。注意，招募领袖会花费£unity£§Y凝聚力§!。如果储备不足，就要等到收集足够后再进行招募。\n\n新总督招募完毕后将会在母星等待安排。"
